180        // 2 - Program priority context
181        $program = $article->getProgram();
182
183        if (!empty($program->getUrlSafeValue()) && in_array($program->getUrlSafeValue(), self::POOOL_PROGRAMS_PRIORITY)) {
184            $pageType = $articleSpecification->isSatisfiedBy($article) ? 'premium' : 'free';
185
186            return sprintf('%s-program-%s', $pageType, $program->getUrlSafeValue());
